      "span_text": "The published dataset of Wilson et al.  from expression profiling in the hippocampus of adult rats with Affymetrix RG-U34A chip was downloaded from the NIH Neuroscience Microarray Consortium http://arrayconsortium.tgen.org/, projects: Koh-7K08NS002068-05-3, Koh-2K08NS002068-04."
